query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `notificationPerformanceSummary` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `notificationType` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `channel` enum('push', 'email', 'sms') NOT NULL,
  `periodStart` timestamp NOT NULL,
  `periodEnd` timestamp NOT NULL,
  `totalSent` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `totalDelivered` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `totalViewed` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `totalClicked` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `totalActioned` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `totalDismissed` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `deliveryRate` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `viewRate` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `clickRate` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `actionRate` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `avgTimeToView` int,
  `avgTimeToClick` int,
  `avgTimeToAction` int,
  `effectivenessScore` int,
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  `updatedAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX `notificationType_idx` (`notificationType`),
  INDEX `channel_idx` (`channel`),
  INDEX `periodStart_idx` (`periodStart`),
  INDEX `periodEnd_idx` (`periodEnd`)
)
